
'''= an informal association of organizations -- colleges, hospitals, social, welfare or counseling agencies, businesses-- who voluntarily join together to exchange knowledge, services, products, personnel, and other resources to accomplish a common goal'''--barter-style. They trade available resources for needed sources without primarily relying on new or outside funding. The goal is the mutual benefit of all network members. [http://www.flipkart.com/challenge-resource-exchange-network-seymour-book-0914797468]


